<Base 
  title="Pimsleur Review 2026: Does Audio-Only Learning Actually Work?"
  description="Honest Pimsleur review for 2026. Learn about pricing, pros, cons, and how it compares to Duolingo and iTalki. Rating: 8.0/10."
